{"tid":1816913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★FBI 調查遇瓶頸　再求助 Apple 解鎖手機","createTime":"2020-01-08T15:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T05:54:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62cce7329176cb3372334425254badc91e26587f","tid":1816913,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"在去年 12 月，美國佛羅里達州的彭薩科拉海軍航空基地發生槍擊事件，兇手為沙烏地阿拉伯皇家空軍的 Mohammed Saeed Alshamrani，他在這場恐怖襲擊中擊殺 3 人，並使 8 個人受傷。現在 FBI 獲取了據信是兇手的兩台 iPhone，但卻無法成功解鎖，因此再度求助於 Apple。<br />\n<br />\n據多家外媒報導指出，FBI 寄給 Apple 法律顧問的信件中，表明他們已經取得了法院同意得以搜索該手機的內容，但因為兩台 iPhone 都有密碼保護，儘管 FBI 的調查人員用猜測的方法來嘗試破解該手機，卻仍然無法成功。<br />\n<br />\n在過去，FBI 就曾求助於 Apple 希望能破解聖貝納迪諾槍擊案兇手的手機，但遭到 Apple 拒絕，<span style=\"color: red;\">最後傳出美國向一家匿名服務提供商求助才成功破解該手機</span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過這次 Apple 很快地就發表了聲明，表示他們已與執法機關進行合作，並且在公開聲明中寫道：「當 FBI 向我們徵求一個月前那起案件的相關資料時，我們就將所有的資料都提供出去了，而我們也會在能力所及的範圍內持續協助他們。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/01/08/fbi-seeks-apple-for-help-again/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2Ffbi-seeks-apple-for-help-again%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IhZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=7056f6c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/01/08/fbi-seeks-apple-for-help-again/</a>"},{"pid":"47ffee92b12765a40326c32234839a696eda3c74","tid":1816913,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6044ab771d6650ce3861ceadf6b1ebef9df2df0b","tid":1816913,"uid":18001,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"支那要求果陣又即刻跪係到含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"